sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para:
The external interfaces are represented by the generated RTE based on the CPD_SstSr.xml sst file. CPD_SstSr.xml is exported from CPD_SST.xlsx with the mapping set in the CPD_SstSr.xsd file.
CPD_SST.xlsx location: https://eu.artifactory.conti.de/artifactory/i_bs_vw_meb_19_icas1_chorus_packages_conan_releases_l/appl/ZV_Lib
CPD_SstSr.xsd location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ZV_Lib/CPD/Evo/cfg/rteCfg/xsd/CPD_SstSr.xsd
CPD_SstSr.xml location: https://github-vni.geo.conti.de/bs-vw-meb-19-icas1-chorus/sw.sys.chorus_main_doc/blob/master/mc_sw/appl/ZV_Lib/CPD/Evo/cfg/rteLight/mirror/CPD_SstSr.xml

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The external dependencies of the component are the library functions.
